"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-sport-tennis-1929508-Rafael-Nadal-Novak-Djokovic-Olympics-2024-retirement\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  Rafael Nadalhit back at retirement questions immediately after losing to Novak Djokovic at the Olympics.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 106, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 75, \"end\": 89, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Novak Djokovic\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The long-time rivals faced off for the 60th time in the second round of the Paris 2024 games.\", \"from\": 107, \"to\": 200, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 183, \"end\": 193, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999999893134, \"rank\": 1.0670772104676157e-11, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But the Spaniardwas no match for the top seed, going out 6-1 6-4in what many fear could be the last singles match of his career.\", \"from\": 202, \"to\": 330, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"After coming off the court, Nadal voiced his exasperation after being quizzed over the end of his career again and explained what would eventually make him hang it up.\", \"from\": 332, \"to\": 499, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 360, \"end\": 365, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 0.9999999987965111, \"rank\": 1.2035969612356775e-09, \"text\": \"Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Asked if he had any thoughts in his mind about whether he had just walked off Court Philippe-Chatrier for the final time, Nadal quipped: \\\"Every day, huh?\", \"from\": 501, \"to\": 654, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 585, \"end\": 602, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippe_Chatrier\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Philippe-Chatrier\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippe_Chatrier\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippe_Chatrier\"}, {\"begin\": 623, \"end\": 628, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 0.9999999987965111, \"rank\": 1.2035969612356775e-09, \"text\": \"Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Every day you want me to retire every day guys.\", \"from\": 655, \"to\": 702, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You ask me for that every single day.\\\"\", \"from\": 703, \"to\": 741, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"While the 22-time Grand Slam champion could not give a real answer about his career expiry date, he shed light on when he might consider quitting.\", \"from\": 743, \"to\": 889, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He continued: \\\"I am trying to do my best every single day.\", \"from\": 890, \"to\": 948, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I answer but I cannot live every single day with the feeling that it's going to be or not going to be my last match.\", \"from\": 949, \"to\": 1065, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I come here, I try my best, I play and when I decide to stop playing or when I decide to keep going, I will let you know.\", \"from\": 1067, \"to\": 1189, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I do not know, I just try my best every single day, trying to enjoy a thing that I have been enjoying for so much time.\\\"\", \"from\": 1190, \"to\": 1310, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Just in:Long-standing WTA event scrapped and worries raised that more will follow  Our community members are treated to special offers, promotions, and adverts from us and our partners.\", \"from\": 1312, \"to\": 1497, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can check out at any time.\", \"from\": 1498, \"to\": 1528, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy Policy    Nadal has spent the better part of two years sidelined through injuries.\", \"from\": 1529, \"to\": 1627, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And he admitted that he would walk away when he felt he was no longer able to meet the level he wanted.\", \"from\": 1628, \"to\": 1731, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have been suffering a lot of injuries the last two years so if I feel that I am not competitive enough to keep going or physically I am not ready enough to keep going, I will stop and I will let you know,\\\" he added.\", \"from\": 1733, \"to\": 1951, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But I mean, I do not think every day about if I am retiring or not.\\\"\", \"from\": 1952, \"to\": 2021, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But when the time to retire does come, Nadal is at peace with the idea.\", \"from\": 2023, \"to\": 2094, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2062, \"end\": 2067, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 0.9999999987965111, \"rank\": 1.2035969612356775e-09, \"text\": \"Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He said: \\\"That's part of life.\", \"from\": 2095, \"to\": 2125, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Everything have a beginning, everything have an end.\", \"from\": 2126, \"to\": 2178, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I will miss playing tennis at the competitive stages as probably all the professionals that have been playing tennis for almost all their lives and they really like what they do.\", \"from\": 2179, \"to\": 2357, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Do not miss:Jack Draper 'not meeting other athletes' at Olympics after making costly mistake  Do not miss:Dan Evans shows true colours with Andy Murray comments after Emma Raducanu snub  Do not miss:Caroline Wozniacki brutally mocks Olympics 2024 opponent mid-point in Paris  We use your sign-up to provide content in ways you have consented to and to improve our understanding of you.\", \"from\": 2359, \"to\": 2744, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2465, \"end\": 2474, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_J._Evans\", \"score\": 0.9559075792513085, \"rank\": 0.04612623777431836, \"text\": \"Dan Evans\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_J._Evans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_J._Evans\"}, {\"begin\": 2499, \"end\": 2510, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.5134375832799388e-47, \"text\": \"Andy Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}, {\"begin\": 2526, \"end\": 2539, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emma_Raducanu\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Emma Raducanu\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emma_Raducanu\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emma_Raducanu\"}, {\"begin\": 2558, \"end\": 2576, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caroline_Wozniacki\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Caroline Wozniacki\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caroline_Wozniacki\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caroline_Wozniacki\"}, {\"begi